Package uniol.apt.compiler

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAptServiceProcessor
    Abstract annotation processor base class which scans for an annotation, analyzes all classes marked by this annotation and writes their names in files in META-INF
    AbstractServiceProcessor
    Abstract annotation processor base class which scans for an annotation, analyzes all classes marked by this annotation and writes their names in files in META-INF
    AbstractSPIServiceProcessor
    Annotation processor generating ServiceLoader-style SPI information in META-INF.
    ModuleProcessor
    Annotation processor which scans for an AptModule annotation, analyzes all classes marked by this annotation and writes their names in a file in META-INF
    MyTypes
    An additional function to work with TypeMirrors
    ParameterTransformationProcessor
    Annotation processor which scans for an AptParameterTransformation annotation, analyzes all classes marked by this annotation and writes their names in a file in META-INF
    ParserProcessor
    Annotation Processor which searches for classes annotated with AptParser, analyzes them and write them in lists in META-INF where the Parsers class can find them.
    RendererProcessor
    Annotation Processor which searches for classes annotated with AptRenderer, analyzes them and write them in lists in META-INF where the Renderers class can find them.
    ReturnValueTransformationProcessor
    Annotation processor which scans for an AptReturnValueTransformation annotation, analyzes all classes marked by this annotation and writes their names in a file in META-INF
